<div class="c230_138">
<div id="v230.138.1"><span class="H3605 s">ALABARTE he con todo</span><span class="H3820 s"> mi corazón</span><span class="H5048 s">: delante</span><span class="H430 s"> de los dioses</span><span class="H2167 s"> te cantaré salmos</span>.</div>
<div id="v230.138.2"><span class="H7812 s">Encorvaréme</span><span class="H1964 s"> al templo</span><span class="H6944 s"> de tu santuario</span><span class="H3034 s">, y alabaré</span><span class="H8034 s"> tu nombre</span><span class="H5921 s"> por</span><span class="H2617 s"> tu misericordia</span><span class="H571 s"> y tu verdad</span><span class="H3588 s">: porque</span><span class="H1431 s"> has hecho magnífico</span><span class="H8034 s"> tu nombre</span><span class="H565 s">, y tu dicho</span><span class="H5921 s"> sobre</span><span class="H3605 s"> todas</span> las cosas.</div>
<div id="v230.138.3"><span class="H3117 s">En el día</span><span class="H7121 s"> que clamé</span><span class="H6030 s">, me respondiste</span><span class="H7292 s">; esforzásteme</span><span class="H5797 s"> con fortaleza</span><span class="H5315 s"> en mi alma</span>.</div>
<div id="v230.138.4"><span class="H3068 s">Confesarte han, oh Jehová</span><span class="H3605 s">, todos</span><span class="H4428 s"> los reyes</span><span class="H776 s"> de la tierra</span><span class="H8085 s">, cuando habrán oído</span><span class="H561 s"> los dichos</span><span class="H6310 s"> de tu boca</span>.</div>
<div id="v230.138.5"><span class="H7891 s">Y cantarán</span><span class="H1870 s"> de los caminos</span><span class="H3068 s"> de Jehová</span><span class="H3519 s">: que la gloria</span><span class="H3068 s"> de Jehová</span><span class="H1419 s"> es grande</span>.</div>
<div id="v230.138.6"><span class="H3588 s">Porque</span><span class="H3068 s"> el alto Jehová</span><span class="H7200 s"> atiende</span><span class="H8217 s"> al humilde</span><span class="H1364 s">; mas al altivo</span><span class="H3045 s"> mira</span><span class="H4801 s"> de lejos</span>.</div>
<div id="v230.138.7"><span class="H518 s">Si</span><span class="H3212 s"> anduviere</span><span class="H7130 s"> yo en medio</span><span class="H6869 s"> de la angustia</span><span class="H2421 s">, tú me vivificarás</span><span class="H5921 s">: contra</span><span class="H639 s"> la ira</span><span class="H341 s"> de mis enemigos</span><span class="H7971 s"> extenderás</span><span class="H3027 s"> tu mano</span><span class="H3225 s">, y salvaráme tu diestra</span>.</div>
<div id="v230.138.8"><span class="H3068 s">Jehová</span><span class="H1584 s"> cumplirá</span><span class="H2617 s"> por mí: tu misericordia</span><span class="H3068 s">, oh Jehová</span><span class="H5769 s">, es para siempre</span><span class="H408 s">; no</span><span class="H4639 s"> dejarás la obra</span><span class="H3027 s"> de tus manos</span>.</div></div>
